    "effect": "Javed’s Swarm allows you to control a great number of insects from the environment. \nUpon casting this spell, a swarm of controlled insects crawls out from nearby crevices and forms a horde with a SPD Statistic of 7 which can engulf a single target by making an attack at a Base 14. \nThis attack deals 1d6 damage to the target’s torso, ignores all worn armor, and has a 100% chance of poisoning. \nThe Horde has 15 Hit Points and a Dodge base of 14.",
